{"tid":1489644,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"個胃好痛，點算好","createTime":"2019-08-20T02:20:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T22:32:24.000Z","uid":159215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b7ad0882c1895ac33c383b4dec9b9c7e557a82f7","tid":1489644,"uid":159215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:20:27.000Z","msg":"我本身一向都有少少胃脹，成日有胃氣出，不過唔係大問題冇理到<br />\n<br />\n前日有d口渴，飲咗支益力多無耐個胃就開始痛，本身諗住普通搞痛瞓返覺冇事，點知到今日都未好<br />\n<br />\n琴日去咗睇醫生開咗d胃藥同打咗支止肚痛針，返到屋企就嘔返哂d午餐出嚟<br />\n<br />\n而家個胃仲好痛，覺都唔係幾瞓到，有冇咩方法可以舒緩吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6ed89c5c07d3875de096c4a1dab76b081862b2d","tid":1489644,"uid":109780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:28:43.000Z","msg":"開咗啲咩胃藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88c09a7dd714cb5d338b6ff4cb9e3b2ad214aca1","tid":1489644,"uid":159215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6ed89c5c07d3875de096c4a1dab76b081862b2d","tid":1489644,"uid":109780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:28:43.000Z","msg":"開咗啲咩胃藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:33:50.000Z","msg":"唔係太識，就咁打化學名算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nHyoscine Methobromide <br />\nFamotidine<br />\nMefenamic acid<br />\nDimehydrinate <br />\nOxethazaine"},{"pid":"80e84532a569df39dede9b2bc5fdd25aa4360ba0","tid":1489644,"uid":109780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:57:57.000Z","msg":"做咩會開NSAID比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n胃痛食止痛藥係冇用㗎<br />\n仲要開會傷胃嘅消炎藥比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咩醫生嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e159ddbf1e6779dd85fb21a1f63bbf912f9d0c04","tid":1489644,"uid":159215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80e84532a5